'''Abdal Salam Al-Dabaji''' (born 24 April 1979 in [[Gaza Governorate|Gaza]]) he is a retired athlete who competed internationally for [[State of Palestine|Palestine]].<ref name="elias">[https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/al/abdal-salam-al-dabaji-1.html Sports-Reference Profile]</ref>

He represented [[Palestine at the 2004 Summer Olympics]] in [[Athens]]. He competed in the 800 metres where he finished 8th in his heat and so failing to advance.<ref name="elias"/>

